### Generic CRUD API Tests
### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@contentType = application/json
# Note: In development with AUTH_BYPASS=true, the Authorization header is optional
# @accessToken = your-access-token-here

### List All Tables
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables
# Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Table Schema - tblAnsatte (Employees)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblAnsatte/schema

### Get Table Schema - tblBestillinger (Orders)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblBestillinger/schema

### Get Table Schema - tblOppskrifter (Recipes)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblOppskrifter/schema

### List Records - Employees
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblAnsatte

### List Records - Employees with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblAnsatte?page=1&page_size=10

### List Records - Employees with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblAnsatte?search=Hansen

### List Records - Employees with Sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblAnsatte?sort_by=Etternavn&sort_desc=false

### Get Single Employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblAnsatte/1

### Create New Employee
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblAnsatte
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "Fornavn": "Kari",
  "Etternavn": "Nordmann",
  "Stilling": "Kokk",
  "Telefon": "98765432",
  "Epost": "kari.nordmann@larvik.kommune.no",
  "Aktiv": true
}

### Update Employee
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblAnsatte/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "Telefon": "91234567",
  "Stilling": "Kjøkkensjef"
}

### Delete Employee
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblAnsatte/1

### List Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblBestillinger?page=1&page_size=20

### Get Single Order
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblBestillinger/1

### Create New Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblBestillinger
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "KundeID": 1,
  "BestillingsDato": "2024-01-15",
  "LeveringsDato": "2024-01-20",
  "AntallPersoner": 50,
  "Status": "Ny",
  "Kommentarer": "Vegetarisk alternativ ønskes"
}

### List Recipes
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblOppskrifter

### Search Recipes
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblOppskrifter?search=fisk

### Get Recipe Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblOppskrifter/1

### Create New Recipe
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblOppskrifter
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "Navn": "Laksemiddag",
  "Beskrivelse": "Ovnsbakt laks med grønnsaker",
  "Kategori": "Hovedrett",
  "AntallPortjoner": 4,
  "Tilberedningstid": 45,
  "Allergener": "Fisk",
  "Naringsinformasjon": "Protein: 25g, Fett: 15g, Karbohydrater: 20g"
}

### List Products/Ingredients
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblProdukter

### Get Product Stock Levels
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblLager

### List Customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblKunder

### Get Customer Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblKunder/1

### List Suppliers
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblLeverandoerer

### List Menu Items
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tables/tblMeny

### Create Menu Item
